Loading and cleaning the dataset

Select variables of interest

visit_data = remove_id %>% 
  dplyr::select(-visit_num, -dayofweek, -facilityname, -postalcode, -facilityzip) %>%
  mutate(mews, mews = ifelse( mews>5, 6, mews)) %>% 
  mutate(mews = as.character(mews)) %>% 
  mutate(mews = recode(mews, `0` = "normal", `1` = "normal", `1` = "normal", `2` = "increase_caution", `3` = "increase_caution", `4` = "further_deterioration", `5` = "further_deterioration", `6` = "immediate_action_required"))
